&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After parsing produces the AST, the next step is to convert it into &lt;strong&gt;ZIR&lt;/strong&gt; (Zig Intermediate Representation). But before we dive into how this works, let&amp;rsquo;s understand &lt;strong&gt;why&lt;/strong&gt; we need ZIR in the first place.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
